title: Woods of Belial - demo compilation
description:
Band: Woods of Belial
Album: Woods of Belial
       A demo tape compilation containing:
       Thy Unholy Pentagram (1996)
       Baxabaxaxaxaxabaxaxaxaxa! 666 Yndstr Draconis (1997)
Release date: 2003
Release media: tape

======== Track list ========

Baxabaxaxaxaxabaxaxaxaxa! 666 Yndstr Draconis:
1. Lunar Triumphator of Evil
2. Into the Woods of Belial (Goatlord Necroemperor)
3. Pervertum: Margat Nepeht Nommus

Thy Unholy Pentagram:
4. Black Vampyyr (The Beast)
5. Winter Darkness of Ahti and the Seven Keys of Evil
6. Forest of the Evil Pentagram


Additional info:
This torrent contains the Woods of Belial demo compilation in two forms:
split into tracks, and as one long file.
The "Woods of Belial - Entire tape" file contains the audio of the tape in its most "untouched" form. The only thing I cut from it was about 20 seconds of silence in the beginning, and quite a lot of silence after the end of the last song. This file also contains a few defects that appear on my copy of the tape: there are 3 places on the tape where the sound drops for a very split second. Since these drops are extremely short, I deleted them from the single tracks, and their absance shouldn't be noticable by the average listener, but if you still want the "uncut" version, you can always edit the "Entire tape" file.
